        }`}>
          Spark
        </h1>
        <span className={`text-[11px] font-bold text-cyan-400/40 uppercase tracking-[1.5em] mt-3 transition-all duration-1000 ${hasHistory ? 'opacity-0' : 'opacity-100'}`}>
          Intelligence
        </span>
      </div>
